Output examples/gifs/reasoning-debug.gif

Set Shell cmd
Set Height 760
Set Width 1450
Set Framerate 18
Set FontSize 26

Hide
  Type `set PATH=%CD%\examples\demo-bin;%PATH% && cls`
  Enter
  Sleep 300ms
Show

Sleep 500ms
Type@25ms `mods --reasoning auto --debug "When should I use each review mode?"`
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 5s
